      "end": 262.03,
      "text": "We had a plan on going to Italy"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.03,
      "end": 265.6,
      "text": "But we had to cancel it the last moment"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.6,
      "end": 266.46,
      "text": "Do you know why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.02,
      "end": 267.3,
      "text": "No"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.3,
      "end": 269.71,
      "text": "Because of your row with Angela"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.71,
      "end": 273.25,
      "text": "We weren't able to go and leave you on your own"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.25,
      "end": 275.35,
      "text": "We had to cancel our holiday"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.35,
      "end": 277.53,
      "text": "And bring you here"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.53,
      "end": 280.27,
      "text": "And now you're going to stay here"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.27,
      "end": 282.2,
      "text": "For good"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.2,
      "end": 283.94,
      "text": "I understand correctly"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.94,
      "end": 285.69,
      "text": "He's forgotten"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.69,
      "end": 287.86,
      "text": "It's amazing"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.86,
      "end": 288.56,
      "text": "Stop it"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.56,
      "end": 292.53,
      "text": "네 물론 이해가 되기는 하지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.53,
      "end": 293.25,
      "text": "만약에"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.25,
      "end": 294.97,
      "text": "What would it be like"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.97,
      "end": 296.87,
      "text": "If Anthony was his father?"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.13,
      "end": 300.73,
      "text": "Then he would speak differently?"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.99,
      "end": 301.49,
      "text": "Maybe?"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.75,
      "end": 304.65,
      "text": "뭔가 좀 더 부드럽게 이야기를 하지 않았을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.91,
      "end": 306.57,
      "text": "Well it depends on their relationship"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.57,
      "end": 309.05,
      "text": "He could be even more angry"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.05,
      "end": 311.21,
      "text": "Maybe he's speaking more carefully"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.21,
      "end": 313.31,
      "text": "Because it's his father-in-law"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.31,
      "end": 314.55,
      "text": "And not his father"
    },
    {
      "start": 314.55,
      "end": 315.69,
      "text": "But"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.69,
      "end": 318.29,
      "text": "그 상황 닥쳐봐야 알지"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.29,
      "end": 320.33,
      "text": "일단 힘든 상황이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.33,
      "end": 321.13,
      "text": "맞습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.13,
      "end": 322.69,
      "text": "취소된 거 속상하지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.69,
      "end": 324.03,
      "text": "He should just"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.03,
      "end": 324.53,
      "text": "You know"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.53,
      "end": 325.31,
      "text": "Speak with that"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.31,
      "end": 326.35,
      "text": "With his wife"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.35,
      "end": 327.69,
      "text": "And be nice"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.69,
      "end": 328.89,
      "text": "To his father-in-law"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.89,
      "end": 329.31,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.31,
      "end": 330.99,
      "text": "He has dementia after all"
    },
    {
      "start": 330.99,
      "end": 331.19,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.19,
      "end": 334.51,
      "text": "유장현님께서 메시지 주셨네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.51,
      "end": 336.77,
      "text": "정현님 크리스님과 함께하는 이 시간"
    },
    {
      "start": 336.77,
      "end": 338.65,
      "text": "너무나도 유익한 시간입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.65,
      "end": 340.23,
      "text": "늘 감사드려요"
    },
    {
      "start": 340.23,
      "end": 342.41,
      "text": "Oh thank you"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.41,
      "end": 343.19,
      "text": "네 감사합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.19,
      "end": 344.35,
      "text": "Thanks to you"
    }
  ]
}